  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Safety and efficacy study in patients with acne vulgaris
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      randomized, double-blind, placebo controlled, parallel-group, multiple-center study to
      evaluate the efficacy and safety of ADPS in the treatment of acne vulgaris.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
